Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~
    `MagicExpansion' shall be an expansion for the MagicUserInterface by
Stefan Stuntz and MagicWB by Martin Huttenloher.  If you haven't already
done so, you should register both products.
    With  `MagicExpansion',   programmers   (for MUI applications)   and
draftsman (for icons) shall be supported.
    This is the second public version of `MagicExpansion'. First
`MagicExpansion' should be Giftware, but I got very few gifts so I
decided that `MagicExpansion' is Shareware now. To become a registered
user, you must pay a little shareware fee of

  DM 15,
  US$ 10,
  or an amount in any other currency which corresponds to US$ 15 (15!),

either cash or in eurocheques. The best way is, to use the included
order form. Send you registration to:

    Johannes Beigel
    Fliederstr. 43a
    65396 Walluf
    GERMANY

    Users in Germany can simply transfer  DM 10 to the following account
(please note, that you want to register for `MagicExpansion'):

    Volksbank Eltville e.V.
    bank code number: 512 910 00
    account number: 71 730

    You'll get the full version of `MagicExpansion'  in the fastest way,
in which are  @{" 4 fonts " Link "FONTS" }  for your own icons.   You mustsn't spread this
full version.
    Registered  users  always get automatically  the  newest versions of
`MagicExpansion'.

@EndNode

