Beigel.  That means you can   (you should)  spread this non-full-version
all  over the world  without  asking  me,    as  long as you don't  take
more than  DM 5,--  or US$ 5,-- for it (including disk and copying costs
but not the postage).
    You are only allowed to spread the whole package.
    If you want  to include files  from this package  in  non-commercial
software  (Shareware,  Freeware,  Giftware...)  you have to  send me the
product.
    If  you  want  to  include  this  package  (or parts of it)  into  a
commercial product you *have* to contact me (address see @{"Introduction" Link "EINLEITUNG" }).

